Tonya Lassus has been a successful Residential Redeveloper at JT Integrity Properties, Inc. since August 2013. The company is part of a nationwide group of thousands of investors helping homeowners out of distressed situations of all kinds.
JT Integrity Properties, Inc. specializes in improving and adding value to real estate properties while creating jobs for people in the community. Under Mrs. Lassus’ skilled leadership and expert guidance, the company has successfully provided services to countless homeowners no matter the situation, area or condition of the home.
Mrs. Lassus and her dedicated team of real estate professionals have established an industry-wide reputation for providing first-class customer service and consistently going above and beyond to meet the unique needs of their clients.
“We will operate our company with integrity and a sense of responsibility to the well-being of our employees, contractors, families and people in NE Indiana,” said Mrs. Lassus.
For her passion and determination in achieve business success grounded in her most personal standards of excellence, Mrs. Lassus is being honored as a role model for professional women in all walks of life.
